                            <b>Help on Active Users</b><p>
                            The active users list contains the names and location of all active members on the board. Your name is added or modified by every action you make. Other users cannot find out any other details if you have kept them private in your profile.<p>
If a non-registered member is active on the board, they will be displayed as a 'Guest'.<p>
To remain on the list, you cannot be 'idle' for more than 15 minutes.
